00:27:32.900 --> 00:27:38.400 align:middle line:84%
So you bounce back all
new, all different, nothing

00:27:38.400 --> 00:27:41.270 align:middle line:84%
to compare it with before,
a refreshing experience.

00:27:41.270 --> 00:27:44.330 align:middle line:90%


